# Server Panel

A customizable server information panel for the ESC menu in **7 Days to Die**  
Fully updated for version **2.1 (b10)** / Alpha 22.

---

## 🧰 Features

- 📋 Adds a slick server info window to the ESC menu
- 🔗 Supports external links (e.g., Discord, GitHub, YouTube)
- 🧱 Modular design using XUi system
- 🌐 English-only localization (optimized UTF-8 support)
- 🖼️ Custom icons and branding

---

## 📦 Files Included

- `ModInfo.xml`  
- `Localization.txt` (English only)  
- `windows.xml` / `xui.xml`  
- `linkURL_1.xml` (remote URL support)  
- `spd_discord.png` + optional icons  

You can rebrand the icons or modify the layout to match your server's style.

---

## 📥 Installation

1. Download or clone this repository.
2. Copy the contents into your 7DTD `Mods` folder:

3. Make sure only one version of the mod is active at a time.
4. Launch the game — the panel appears in the ESC menu.

